<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Posts Top</title>
</head>
<body>
<header>
<%= render 'partial/header' %>
</header>

    <% if user_signed_in? %>
      <%= render 'partial/current_user_area' %>
    <% end %>

<main>
  <div class="w-[90%] max-w-[1200px] mx-auto mt-[50px] text-center">
    <div class="w-full py-[20px] text-center">
      <p class="text-[14px] text-gray-400">Published January 13, 2021</p>
      <h1 class="font-extrabold text-[32px]">7 Rules of Effective Branding</h1>
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-[14px] py-[10px] text-gray-500">Why Branding Matters to your Business</h2>
      <div class="py-[10px] flex flex-wrap md:justify-center justify-start items-center gap-2">
        <div class="inline-block px-2 py-2 bg-gray-200 font-medium leading-tight rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg">Branding</div>
        <div class="inline-block px-2 py-2 bg-gray-200 font-medium leading-tight rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg">Communication</div>
        <div class="inline-block px-2 py-2 bg-gray-200 font-medium leading-tight rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg">Experience</div>
        <div class="inline-block px-2 py-2 bg-gray-200 font-medium leading-tight rounded shadow-md hover:bg-gray-400 hover:shadow-lg">Identity</div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full mt-[20px]">
        <%= image_tag 'demo.jpg', class: 'object-cover w-full h-auto' %>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[20px] w-[80%] mx-auto text-left">
       <p class="font-semibold text-[16px] leading-[1.5em]">Today, I'd like to share an internal project which I recently worked on together with the team – our new Blog.</p>
       <p class="font-semibold text-[16px] leading-[1.5em] mt-[20px]">Clean, minimalistic and content-focused was our main goal for this design direction. What are your thoughts on this?</p>
       <p class="font-semibold text-[16px] leading-[1.5em] mt-[20px] text-gray-400">...And it's already live. Go check out the Fintory Blog here!
        Are you looking to build a web or mobile application?
        We’re always looking to partner with great companies. Say hi at hello@fintory.com</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<footer></footer>

</body>
</html>
